title: The Denzels - Converse Rubber Tracks: Oh Hello
description:
Meet The Denzels, a five piece who came together after three members migrated from California and met their current bandmates once they arrived on the east coast. What started out as long jam sessions turned into a full-fledged band. Listen to the band talk about their background and their experiences in the studio and at Converse Rubber Tracks. 
For more on Converse Rubber Tracks, check out:
www.converse.com/rubbertracks
